Greek Chickpea Salad for episode 2 of Spoon Salads! ü•Ñü•ó If you missed episode 1, this series is all about chopped salads that you can eat with a spoon, which IMO are the BEST kind of salads.

GREEK CHICKPEA SALAD:

Salad:

1 15 oz can chickpeas (garbanzo beans), drained and rinsed
1 ¬Ω cups diced cucumber
1 ¬Ω cups diced bell pepper
1 cup halved cherry tomatoes
¬Ω cup pitted olives, roughly chopped (kalamata, castelvetrano, etc)
Optional: 1/3 cup chopped pepperoncini peppers
¬Ω cup crumbled feta cheese (regular or vegan)

Vinaigrette:

1/2 cup olive oil
3 tbsp red wine vinegar
Juice from ¬Ω of a lemon (~1 tbsp)
1 tsp dijon mustard
¬Ω tsp garlic powder
¬Ω tsp dried oregano
¬º tsp salt
¬º tsp black pepper

Full instructions on our website! #greeksalad #salad #saladsoftiktok #choppedsalad
